5 Uses of Detection

1 Face Unlock (Mobile Security)
    Unlock phone using face recognition
2 CCTV Surveillance
    Detect suspicious activity in public places
3 Self-Driving Cars
    Detect pedestrians, vehicles, traffic signals
4 Attendance System
    Automatically mark attendance using face
5 Retail/Shopping Analysis
    Track customer movement and behavior

Designed Solution: Smart Attendance System
Problem:
Manual attendance takes time and may have errors.

Solution:
Use face detection system to automate attendance.

Working:
Camera captures student faces
System detects and recognizes faces
Attendance is marked automatically
Data is stored in database

Advantages
* Saves time
* Accurate
* No manual work
* Prevents proxy attendance